condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement: Schedule 2, Section V, 1(a) | Description :Except as the Bank shall otherwise agree, HVEN shallnot incur any debt unless a reasonable forecast of revenues and expenditures shows that the estimated net revenues of HVEN foreachFiscal Year during the term of the debt to be incurred shall be at least 1.2 times the estimated debt service requirements ofHVEN in such year on all debt including the debt to be incurred. | Frequency: YEARLY

Loan Agreement: Schedule 2, Section I, C 1 (a) | Description: The Borrower shall and shall cause HVEN to apply to all activitiesunder the Project the criteria, policies, procedures, and arrangements set out in the ESIA, site-specific EMPs, the RPF, and RAPs.| Frequency: CONTINOUS

Loan Agreement: Schedule 2, Section I, C 1 (a) | Description: The Borrower shall and shall cause the HVEN to apply to allactivities under the Project the criteria, policies, procedures, and arrangements set out in EMPs, the RPF, and the RAPs (ifrequired). | Frequency: CONTINUOUS

Loan Agreement: Schedule 2, Section V, 1(a) | Description: Except as the Bank shall otherwise agree, HVEN shall not incur any debtunless a reasonable forecast of the revenues and expenditures of HVEN shows that the estimated net revenues of HVEN for each FiscalYear during the term of the debt to be incurred shall be at least 1.2 times the estimated debt service requirements of HVEN in suchyear on all debt of HVEN including the debt to be incurred. | Frequency: YEARLY
